## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible strategies for crime reduction. The effectiveness of the proposed strategies can vary significantly depending on the specific social, economic, and cultural context of a region. Additionally, the report relies on secondary data, which may not capture the most recent developments in crime reduction strategies.

